{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_QC02_REG_630.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0xf,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "It's too dangerous to go without Regina."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0xd4,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Daaamn, this is a lot.<CR>I guess we better get started."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "The slags here aren't too dangerous, right?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0xd6,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "Right. But if you leave them be,<CR>you might trip on them, so they're<CR>kind of dangerous that way..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "Plus, they fill up all the holes we dig!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x8,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "I'm sure it's just instinct, but they go around filling in holes and cracks with something they secrete from their butt."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x9,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "I mean, they fill up all our holes.<CR>It's a real problem when they fill<CR>up our passages."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0xf,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "This ruin might've been made by slags. Like, it could be the consolidation of all their secretions."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "That's unbelievable. How many hundreds of years would it take them to make it?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x9,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "Even so, it might be more realistic than to think some guy made it out of a big lump of rock."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0xa,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "C'mon! If we take it too easy,<CR>the other guys'll kill our prey."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "Shall we get going, Ayesha?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x193,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "Yes... But I kinda feel bad for them..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0xd4,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "You shouldn't. They multiply and just keep coming."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0xd6,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "If I worried about that every time,<CR>it would cost me my job."
        }
    ]
}